### Describe the issue

Calling request.fileio.streamFile on large files (that are meant to be "excerpted" using HTTP range headers) the NIOCore/ByteBuffer-core throw fatal errors trying to unwrap a nil Optional value.

### Vapor version

4.110.2

### Operating system and version

iOS 26.1

### Swift version

swift-driver version: 1.127.14.1 Apple Swift version 6.2.1 (swiftlang-6.2.1.4.8 clang-1700.4.4.1)

